# CHANGELOG

## v1

Initial Release


## v2

- Added support for autoreloading deployment on doppler config update
- Added support for cleaning kube deployments based on shared / env templates

## v2.1

- Support for branch ID was removed due to frequent collisions
- Support for branch Hash was added
- Fixed issue with workflows checking out wrong platform version. Introduced support for 'platform_version'

## v2.2
- Added support for running E2E action

## v2.3
- Fixed issue with e2e workflow where app was unable to start.
